Your Highness is a 2011 American stoner comic fantasy film directed by David Gordon Green , and stars Danny McBride , James Franco , Natalie Portman , Zooey Deschanel and Justin Theroux .
Written by McBride and Ben Best , the film was released on April 8 , 2011 .
The film received negative reviews from critics and was a box office bomb , grossing $ 28 million worldwide against a $ 50 million budget .